The following command creates a new project myproject which can deploy applications to namespace mynamespace of cluster 
https://kubernetes.default.svc. The permitted Git source repository is set to the url

argocd proj create myproject -d https://kubernetes.default.svc,default -s https://github.com/shubham-gann/argo-assignment

Resource for Project: https://argo-cd.readthedocs.io/en/stable/user-guide/projects/

Resource for kustomize: https://kubebyexample.com/learning-paths/argo-cd/argo-cd-working-kustomize